{"__type":"$$EventMessageAiNode","id":"222d7c0c-2c53-4e3a-8aea-808e8de7fe2b","ts":"2026-03-05T03:48:23.808-05:00","eventName":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","message":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","payload":{"executionId":"4","nodeName":"OpenAI Chat Model3","workflowName":"game_builder_workflow","nodeType":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","workflowId":"XajLsYwviKQDLrmt","msg":"{\"messages\":[\"System: You are a browser game developer.\\n\\nUsing the provided game plan, generate a playable browser game.\\n\\nRequirements:\\n- Use HTML5 Canvas\\n- Use vanilla JavaScript\\n- Implement the controls from the plan\\n- Implement obstacle spawning\\n- Implement collision detection\\n- Implement score tracking\\n- Implement a game loop using requestAnimationFrame\\n\\nGenerate three files:\\n\\n1. index.html\\n2. style.css\\n3. game.js\\n\\nReturn the files in this exact format:\\n\\nINDEX.HTML\\n---\\n<code>\\n---\\n\\nSTYLE.CSS\\n---\\n<code>\\n---\\n\\nGAME.JS\\n---\\n<code>\\n---\\nHuman: Game plan:\\n\\n{\\\"output\\\":{\\\"gameType\\\":\\\"Browser Game\\\",\\\"framework\\\":\\\"HTML, CSS, JavaScript\\\",\\\"controls\\\":[\\\"Arrow Keys for Movement\\\",\\\"Spacebar for Action\\\",\\\"Mouse for Navigation\\\"],\\\"mechanics\\\":[\\\"Collecting Items\\\",\\\"Avoiding Obstacles\\\",\\\"Level Progression\\\",\\\"Scoring System\\\"],\\\"gameLoop\\\":\\\"Player navigates through levels, collects items, avoids obstacles, and scores points until the game ends.\\\",\\\"files\\\":[\\\"index.html\\\",\\\"style.css\\\",\\\"script.js\\\",\\\"assets/\\\"]}}\\n\\nGenerate the full implementation.\"],\"options\":{\"openai_api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini\",\"temperature\":0.2,\"max_retries\":2,\"configuration\":{\"defaultHeaders\":{\"openai-platform\":\"org-qkmJQuJ2WnvoIKMr2UJwIJkZ\"},\"baseURL\":\"https://api.openai.com/v1\",\"fetchOptions\":{\"dispatcher\":{\"_events\":{},\"_eventsCount\":0}}},\"model_kwargs\":{},\"supports_strict_tool_calling\":false,\"use_responses_api\":true},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"Sure! Below are the three files needed to create a simple browser game based on your game plan.\\n\\nINDEX.HTML\\n---\\n```html\\n<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n    <title>Collect and Avoid Game</title>\\n    <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"style.css\\\">\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n    <canvas id=\\\"gameCanvas\\\"></canvas>\\n    <div id=\\\"score\\\">Score: 0</div>\\n    <script src=\\\"game.js\\\"></script>\\n</body>\\n</html>\\n```\\n---\\n\\nSTYLE.CSS\\n---\\n```css\\nbody {\\n    display: flex;\\n    flex-direction: column;\\n    align-items: center;\\n    justify-content: center;\\n    height: 100vh;\\n    margin: 0;\\n    background-color: #f0f0f0;\\n}\\n\\ncanvas {\\n    border: 1px solid #000;\\n}\\n\\n#score {\\n    font-size: 24px;\\n    margin-top: 10px;\\n}\\n```\\n---\\n\\nGAME.JS\\n---\\n```javascript\\nconst canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\\nconst ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\\ncanvas.width = 800;\\ncanvas.height = 600;\\n\\nlet player = {\\n    x: canvas.width / 2,\\n    y: canvas.height - 30,\\n    width: 30,\\n    height: 30,\\n    speed: 5,\\n};\\n\\nlet items = [];\\nlet obstacles = [];\\nlet score = 0;\\nlet gameOver = false;\\n\\nfunction spawnItem() {\\n    const x = Math.random() * (canvas.width - 20);\\n    items.push({ x: x, y: 0, width: 20, height: 20 });\\n}\\n\\nfunction spawnObstacle() {\\n    const x = Math.random() * (canvas.width - 50);\\n    obstacles.push({ x: x, y: 0, width: 50, height: 50 });\\n}\\n\\nfunction detectCollision(rect1, rect2) {\\n    return rect1.x < rect2.x + rect2.width &&\\n           rect1.x + rect1.width > rect2.x &&\\n           rect1.y < rect2.y + rect2.height &&\\n           rect1.y + rect1.height > rect2.y;\\n}\\n\\nfunction update() {\\n    if (gameOver) return;\\n\\n    ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);\\n\\n    // Move player\\n    if (keys['ArrowLeft'] && player.x > 0) player.x -= player.speed;\\n    if (keys['ArrowRight'] && player.x < canvas.width - player.width) player.x += player.speed;\\n\\n    // Update items and obstacles\\n    items.forEach(item => {\\n        item.y += 2;\\n        if (detectCollision(player, item)) {\\n            score++;\\n            items.splice(items.indexOf(item), 1);\\n        }\\n    });\\n\\n    obstacles.forEach(obstacle => {\\n        obstacle.y += 3;\\n        if (detectCollision(player, obstacle)) {\\n            gameOver = true;\\n        }\\n    });\\n\\n    // Remove off-screen items and obstacles\\n    items = items.filter(item => item.y < canvas.height);\\n    obstacles = obstacles.filter(obstacle => obstacle.y < canvas.height);\\n\\n    // Draw player\\n    ctx.fillStyle = 'blue';\\n    ctx.fillRect(player.x, player.y, player.width, player.height);\\n\\n    // Draw items\\n    ctx.fillStyle = 'green';\\n    items.forEach(item => ctx.fillRect(item.x, item.y, item.width, item.height));\\n\\n    // Draw obstacles\\n    ctx.fillStyle = 'red';\\n    obstacles.forEach(obstacle => ctx.fillRect(obstacle.x, obstacle.y, obstacle.width, obstacle.height));\\n\\n    // Update score\\n    document.getElementById('score').innerText = `Score: ${score}`;\\n}\\n\\nconst keys = {};\\nwindow.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {\\n    keys[e.key] = true;\\n});\\nwindow.addEventListener('keyup', (e) => {\\n    keys[e.key] = false;\\n});\\n\\nfunction gameLoop() {\\n    update();\\n    if (!gameOver) {\\n        requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\\n    } else {\\n        ctx.fillStyle = 'black';\\n        ctx.font = '48px Arial';\\n        ctx.fillText('Game Over', canvas.width / 2 - 100, canvas.height / 2);\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n// Start the game\\nsetInterval(spawnItem, 1000);\\nsetInterval(spawnObstacle, 2000);\\ngameLoop();\\n```\\n--- \\n\\nThis implementation creates a simple game where the player can move left and right using the arrow keys, collect green items to score points, and avoid red obstacles. The game ends when the player collides with an obstacle, and the score is displayed on the screen.\"}]]},\"tokenUsageEstimate\":{\"completionTokens\":1006,\"promptTokens\":224,\"totalTokens\":1230}}}"}}
